        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/11443\">https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/11443</a> is the update in wasmtime to this tag, thanks again for it!</p>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/11443\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://uploads.zulipusercontent.&quot;)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/11443\" title=\"Update WASIp3 WITs to a tagged release by alexcrichton · Pull Request #11443 · bytecodealliance/wasmtime\">Update WASIp3 WITs to a tagged release by alexcrichton · Pull Request #11443 · bytecodealliance/wasmtime</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">Now that there's an official tag it's best to use that, and this'll help keep everything in sync as well.</div></div></div>",
